Merged PR 19566: fix(WPO-13252): Fix truncated Annotation document body.

# List the JIRA items included in this pull request  #
[WPO-13252 - Contact note template files get truncated on deployment](https://wealthdynamixltd.atlassian.net/browse/WPO-13252)

# Description #
The WDX packaging data exporter runs a Dynamics query to export Annotations. To do this, it uses the core `CrmHelper`. That in turn had `Distinct` hard-coded `true`.

Now, due to a bug in Dynamics regarding how it executes the query with 'distict' in the DB, the `documentbody` attribute gets truncated to 2,000 chars.

The workaround fix is to set `Distinct = false` in the case when the query is for Annotation and `documentbody` is one of the attributes requested in the "DataConfig.json".
